    MODULE=GraphicsMagick
   VERSION=1.3.47
    SOURCE=$MODULE-$VERSION.tar.xz
SOURCE_URL=$SFORGE_URL/graphicsmagick
SOURCE_VFY=sha256:95fb682dab0206a9db168d065963f4ffdf5a60b0b2a375aca1f4492fb18d0627
  WEB_SITE=http://www.graphicsmagick.org/
   ENTERED=20061117
   UPDATED=20260601
     SHORT="A swiss army knife of image processing"

cat << EOF
GraphicsMagick is the swiss army knife of image processing. It provides a robust
collection of tools and libraries which support reading, writing, and
manipulating an image in over 88 major formats including important formats like
DPX, GIF, JPEG, JPEG-2000, PNG, PDF, SVG, and TIFF.
GraphicsMagick supports huge images on systems that support large files, and has
been tested with gigapixel-size images.
EOF
